This is a simple C++ project that I am going to use as a start point for compilation and debugging C++ 
project via Visual Studio Code.



### Links
   - https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/debugtest/tasks
   - https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/cpp/launch-json-reference
   - https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/cpp/customize-cpp-settings
   
   - https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/reference/variables-reference
       ${workspaceFolder}         -> Path of the folder opened in VS Code
       ${fileDirname}             -> Currently opened file's folder path
       ${fileBasenameNoExtension} -> Currently opened file's basename with no file extension

   - https://microsin.net/programming/arm/vscode-ccpppropertiesjson-reference.html
